title: Candlewood Lake Rental
posting_body: ['DIRECT WATERFRONT - CANDLEWOOD LAKE - 12 Month Lease or 6 to 9 Month Lease available at $3,750', 'YEAR ROUND UNFURNISHED OR FURNISHED 3-4 BD/3 full BA easy living comfortable country contemporary with flexible floor plan.', 'Multi-level Decks - w/huge awning and Gazebo for different areas to read, entertain or just plain relax!', "Water's edge Deck & Dock.", 'Bring your boat/kayaks/canoes.', 'Large spacious rooms-fully equipment.', 'Main Level offers a large Dining Room & Living Room with a wall of doors off to an oversized deck w/huge retractable awning.', 'Eat-In Kitchen also offers access to Deck.', 'Updated fully equipment Kitchen with granite counters & pantry.', 'A full bath rounds out the ML.', 'UL hosts the primary bedroom w/walk-in closets and private balcony plus full BA. 2 secondary bedrooms and full bath.', 'Finished walk out lower level offers additional flex space for office/family room/exercise etc.', 'Easy access to all points South!', 'Renter pays the following utilities: Electric, Propane, Oil, Internet, Lawn, Snow Removal, Insurance', 'Owner pays for property taxes, water & septic.']
